Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.55,0:00:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,難道告白成功了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.62,0:00:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,傻瓜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.69,0:00:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,一定又被騙了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.91,0:00:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你真傻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.27,0:00:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,他們希望被我玩弄
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.04,0:00:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,男人都一個德行
